After installing a fresh copy of Mac OS X:

- Start FileVault (if on a mobile device)

- Install the latest version of Xcode

- Install the latest version of MacPorts

- Install selected ports:

    sudo port -F <ports-file>

- Run the scripts in the after directory

- Install the must-have applications:

    Quicksilver
    http://www.blacktree.com/

    MagiCal
    http://www.charcoaldesign.co.uk/magical

    SlimBatteryMonitor
    http://www.orange-carb.org/SBM/

    MenuMeters
    http://www.ragingmenace.com/software/menumeters/

    MacTeX (TeXLive)
    http://www.tug.org/mactex/

    bibtex2html
    http://www.lri.fr/~filliatr/bibtex2html/
